      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　てっきり「そうですね。私は認めてませんが」\nみたいなことを言われると思ったんだが",
      "startTime": 24.202391718568073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
