      "text": "茶化さないで下さい！　言いませんよ\nそんなことは……もう",
      "startTime": 29.39020641501165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。ってことは、俺はようやく琴乃に\nマネージャーとして認められたってことかな",
      "startTime": 35.24488547454555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 37.99878577997565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
