      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_03-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "はい。時々家に帰ってきた時に\nアイドルのこととか、寮でのこととか",
      "startTime": 139.36431068726384,
